headline.main: GDYNIA LINE ADDING SIX NEW VESSELS; Four Now Being Built for the Polish Company's Services to Atlantic Ports MANAGING DIRECTOR HERE Leszczynski, Just Back From Tour of American Agencies, Will Sail Thursday Aleksander Leszczynski, managing director of the Gdynia America Line, returned to New York last night after a hurried tour of the United States and Canada for a series of conferences with travel men and agents of the line. He expects to sail for home next Thursday.
